and when I asked, how many here have met God, I got a few people saying,
&quot;me&quot; guess, I ask some pretty dump questions, eh&quot; I counted 5 me&#39;s, and some
that haven&#39;t I guess.



In a message dated 5/10/2009 8:32:14 A.M. Eastern Daylight Time,
ckmorris95@... writes:



Snow - In the Goldwave software you can &#39;save as&quot; mp3.  Directly under the
file name in the &quot;Save As&quot; where you name your clip is &quot;File Format&quot;.  Click
on the drop down list arrow and MP3 should be your 2nd choice on the list.
Click MP3 and save.  Your file is now in MP3 format. :-)  I hope this helps.

